{"tid":2324163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華疑臨時甩底激嬲大陸網紅報警 網民撐偶像轟炒作","createTime":"2020-12-13T17:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T23:37:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b21ef974464e61998992d81ac504a080cd6a5197","tid":2324163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T17:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1I7AVd0Budr_NrM98Oe0TCf3voE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DVY63KQUZBM7J466VUL47NWBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1I7AVd0Budr_NrM98Oe0TCf3voE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DVY63KQUZBM7J466VUL47NWBA.jpg&h=6c80c3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年香港藝人到大陸掘金興起直播帶貨熱潮，先後有不少港星參與，包括曾志偉、蔡少芬、任達華等都曾現身支持，連天王劉德華亦加入行列，正在大陸為聖誕檔期上映的新片《拆彈專家2》宣傳的他，今月初與大陸知名女主播薇婭一同做直播sell貨，打正旗號明星來了吸引網友，結果66萬張戲票迅速售罄，可見反應熱烈，令首次參與的華仔難以置信：「我覺得很假！」<br />\n<br />\n這邊廂大受歡迎的華仔，近日卻被另一名網絡紅人「舞帝利哥」報警告他毀約，消息指華仔答應出席「舞帝利哥」的直播活動，當事人早前為招客，還分享《拆彈專家2》導演邱禮濤的祝福片段，以作宣傳，想不到華仔臨時甩底，令「舞帝利哥」如意算盤打不響，損失慘重，一怒之下，「舞帝利哥」到廣州一間派出所報案，並於微博寫上：「關於天王巨星採訪活動的事，我在等結果&hellip;&hellip;」他展示一張報案後回條，顯示于利先生（即舞帝利哥）於12月9日報案，並獲單位登記受理，但該文件上沒有提到案情詳情。<br />\n<br />\n不少華仔fans表示不相信華仔沒有誠信，直指「舞帝利哥」此舉是借華仔炒作，自我宣傳，有聰明的華仔fans更留言：「若真有活動，華仔天地會有宣慱。」他們又批評「舞帝利哥」去報警行為誇張：「合同違約是民事糾紛，不是刑事案件，用報警？」另一方面，有網民批評華仔甩底冇合約精神，「明星也不過如此，契約可以隨時撕毁，法律的红綫隨便踩。」華仔沒有就事件回應，但有報道指《拆彈專家2》的官方微博曾為此發文澄清：「劉德華先生沒有經紀人，不要認為電影片方否了就說是個人行為，劉德華只有華仔天地個人官網，請那個利利的朋友再不要拿此炒作，以免到時間下不來台」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201213/V3SJ6VMP3NGBLBX6R6ENFUE3QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201213%2FV3SJ6VMP3NGBLBX6R6ENFUE3QA%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=cf6e2850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201213%2FV3SJ6VMP3NGBLBX6R6ENFUE3QA%2F&h=c0eb233a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201213/V3SJ6VMP3NGBLBX6R6ENFUE3QA/</a>"},{"pid":"d742b1520905df6db7a419fa69f21f9c7584fc49","tid":2324163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T17:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5jQM01kF_C_Ad5pmvFm7sOUdXNE=/802x602/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GUARXKE66JCOBPELXBA2LYOEHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5jQM01kF_C_Ad5pmvFm7sOUdXNE%3D%2F802x602%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGUARXKE66JCOBPELXBA2LYOEHQ.jpg&h=99958340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4c-IirTN3vRGNQyGfIG10upmnHs=/802x659/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/STFDZ2ZIIVHMBIEPNMOBK7RWDQ.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4c-IirTN3vRGNQyGfIG10upmnHs%3D%2F802x659%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSTFDZ2ZIIVHMBIEPNMOBK7RWDQ.PNG&h=d2a41077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4li2Hi0q9Se5d5rLttDzfAmMgpI=/802x1426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S4NQMQFBL5AJRP2ANM72CKK3CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4li2Hi0q9Se5d5rLttDzfAmMgpI%3D%2F802x1426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS4NQMQFBL5AJRP2ANM72CKK3CE.jpg&h=b8ea92fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1EFD4HoIidu3zQBMsaAIKIHEyT0=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HXM77AVIWVBQ5LIQQKKYHPE4HA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1EFD4HoIidu3zQBMsaAIKIHEyT0%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHXM77AVIWVBQ5LIQQKKYHPE4HA.jpg&h=2a652249&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bdcc44c6bc4c30f6f6032e3bd130f1503ff1518","tid":2324163,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T18:09:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得很假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368ffc180c7b341f9d70286645ff25fd432364fe","tid":2324163,"uid":95520,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"無問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩踩法律紅線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜支那有法律㗎咩"},{"pid":"0588cf97acc0fb821e4af4ebadcd1b41d13e32db","tid":2324163,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T18:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他們又批評「舞帝利哥」去報警行為誇張：「合同違約是民事糾紛，不是刑事案件，用報警？」另一方面，有網民批評華仔甩底冇合約精神，「明星也不過如此，契約可以隨時撕毁，法律的红綫隨便踩。」</blockquote>根據香港肥佬黎case<br />\n合同違反係=刑事詐騙<br />\n<br />\n梗係要報驚"},{"pid":"91afbc5fe62ab7e39ddf9126b3c349dc6f651ce5","tid":2324163,"uid":301050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"368ffc180c7b341f9d70286645ff25fd432364fe","tid":2324163,"uid":95520,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"無問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩踩法律紅線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜支那有法律㗎咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T18:19:51.000Z","msg":"尋釁滋事<br />\n拉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceb9b327d022e4107c804fe90561d317d82e62e","tid":2324163,"uid":199736,"like":3,"disli